 It's tough for me to say since I don't have domain knowledge

12:09.040 --> 12:14.040
 in AI to know everything that could or might occur.

12:14.960 --> 12:19.720
 I know, sort of in my own case,

12:19.720 --> 12:22.840
 that most people don't see any of that.

