 I mean, that's what people mostly do.

12:47.080 --> 12:49.960
 I do a bunch of that too because, you know,

12:49.960 --> 12:52.520
 that's what you do in normal life.

12:52.520 --> 12:57.080
 But I've always been completely fascinated

12:57.080 --> 13:00.200
 by the stuff that doesn't fit.

